Package com.CZ2002.interfaces

package com.CZ2002.interfaces
Provides the interfaces used throughout the application.

This package provides the necessary interfaces that form the abstractions in the application. This package also provides functionality to format a String to GregorianCalendar and Date instances through IGregorianCalendarFormattable and IDateFormattable respectively.
